ZH: 请你转达这个消息给他。
EN: Please convey this message to him.

ZH: 我会转达你的意见给老板。
EN: I will convey your opinion to the boss.

ZH: 我需要你转达这个请求给所有员工。
EN: I need you to transmit this request to all employees.

ZH: 转达我的问候给你的父母。
EN: Convey my greetings to your parents.

ZH: 请你转达我们的感谢给他们。
EN: Please convey our gratitude to them.

ZH: 我需要你转达一封重要的信函。
EN: I need you to deliver an important letter.

ZH: 他专门负责转达公司的决策。
EN: He is specifically responsible for conveying the company's decisions.

ZH: 他的任务是把社区的意见转达给政府。
EN: His task is to convey the community's opinions to the government.

ZH: 请你转达我对他的祝福。
EN: Please convey my blessings to him.

ZH: 作为班长，应该能够准确转达老师的意思。
EN: As the class monitor, you should be able to accurately convey the teacher's intentions.

ZH: 他是一个很好的转达者，经常帮助双方沟通。
EN: He is a good intermediary and often helps both parties communicate.

ZH: 我们需要一个能够有效转达信息的新闻发言人。
EN: We need a spokesperson who can effectively transmit information.

ZH: 请你转达给他，会议时间变动了。
EN: Please convey to him that the meeting time has changed.

ZH: 这是我转达给你的最新消息。
EN: This is the latest news I am transmitting to you.

ZH: 你可以用邮件转达这个通知。
EN: You can convey this notice by email.

ZH: 他忠实地转达了顾客的抱怨。
EN: He faithfully conveyed the customer's complaints.

ZH: 转达一份道歉信给客户。
EN: Convey an apology letter to the customer.

ZH: 请你转达我对他的邀请。
EN: Please convey my invitation to him.

ZH: 我们需要一个能够准确转达信息的专业翻译。
EN: We need a professional translator who can accurately convey information.

ZH: 他的任务是将公司的发展战略转达给所有部门。
EN: His task is to convey the company's development strategy to all departments.
